title: Eminent Domain
description: Mitzy Neuhaus is dying to get back to business as usual, but The Worst Economy Since The Great Depression has just about killed home sales in Portland. With all her resources tied up in the inn she and her fiance are opening, she doesn't have a spare dollar, or minute, for her true selling houses. When the excessive interest of the FBI, city planners, and possibly organized crime, threaten to derail Mitzy's business plans, her life goes from crazy to downright deadly.
author: Traci Tyne Hilton
